title: PSP-IPΔ1: Extend PSP staking lockup period
body:
Extend PSP staking lockup period to an epoch length or more to better align stakers' incentives.

Full proposal here: https://gov.paraswap.network/t/psp-ip-1-extend-psp-staking-lockup-period/21
